text: Eddie Younger was a former player for the New York Rens. He is a member of the New York City Basketball Hall of Fame. Younger attended Benjamin Franklin High School and later Long Island University. Younger would also play for the Scranton Miners in the American Basketball League. ==References== Category:Year of birth missing Category:Year of death missing Category:American men's basketball players Category:LIU Brooklyn Blackbirds men's basketball players Category:New York Renaissance players
